   58|       | * We pass the information about the input stream encoding with the
   59|       | * STREAM-START token.
   60|       | *
   61|       | * The next two tokens are responsible for tags:
   62|       | *
   63|       | *      VERSION-DIRECTIVE(major,minor)
   64|       | *      TAG-DIRECTIVE(handle,prefix)
   65|       | *
   66|       | * Example:
