   73|       | * The corresponding sequence of tokens:
   74|       | *
   75|       | *      STREAM-START(utf-8)
   76|       | *      VERSION-DIRECTIVE(1,1)
   77|       | *      TAG-DIRECTIVE("!","!foo")
   78|       | *      TAG-DIRECTIVE("!yaml","tag:yaml.org,2002:")
